IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Julie Ann GAYNOR and William Jeffrey Gaynor Upon the Petition of Julie Ann Gaynor n/k/a Julie Ann Meyer, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning William Jeffrey Gaynor, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-2062 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A former wife appeals an order modifying the child support and postsecondary-education subsidy provisions of the dissolution decree. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
